items.title: 7 cops shot one after the other while responding to call for help from apartment
items.description: Seven police officers have been shot one after the other after responding to a call made from inside a home in San Antonio, Texas, police said.

items.title: California fires live updates: New LA County fire explodes to over 10,000 acres
items.description: At least 28 people are believed to be dead and more than a dozen others remain unaccounted for as multiple wildfires rage across Southern California.

items.title: Russia 'very closely' monitoring Trump's sanctions threats, Kremlin says
items.description: "We carefully record all the nuances," Kremlin spokesperson Dmitry Peskov said.
